The paper proposes a method for multi-view recognition using Convolutional Neural Networks, which is a popular approach in computer vision and machine learning (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG). The paper addresses the problem of active recognition, which involves optimizing trajectories, suggesting a focus on robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of pairwise relationships, which is a common approach in machine learning and computer vision (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the use of image sequences, which suggests a focus on graphics (cs.GR).
